Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明野美星  修學旅行結束回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色友人  六花亭的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.41,0:00:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油三明治  當地的kitty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木雕人偶和鑰匙圈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北海道產的石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  我還帶來了這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吸吸看…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北海道的香氣…聞到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  回家路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  草哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就按照預定計畫好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過身體沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事哦  那麼就11點在站前廣場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼怎麼  明天有什麼事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得…為什麼要問我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是放假呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是在白天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  反正是以前就認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道小夜學姐也一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天？  我沒有什麼計劃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我倒是覺得沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說下  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說為什麼大家都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦  我是為了大八木啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…被江戶川同學喊過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先…先說清楚了  我只是碰巧過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是來買書順便過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快看  來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼來看就是在約會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得變得好像是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我也差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都來到這裡了  就只有一路跟到底了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們打算去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在到了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部…部長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓  噓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是是是是要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也超想跟著他們去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說噓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道這樣…昨天好好問問他們的計劃就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒辦法啊  現在是要跟著這邊的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過總覺得果然草間老師才是理解她的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…也不是這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去站前取照片的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得奇怪就跟過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…你們在想什…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓  喂  要下車了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是這樣的組合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎  草哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  大概是錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊…只是從這邊路過而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們再往深處去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿高跟鞋走這條路好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概還有一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  今年我們也來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  大吃一驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我的話就一起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全…我完全不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔…怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀測會回家的路上出了交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是現在這個時節
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著說今年要一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果媽媽總是因為太忙來不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像總是自己一個人來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  讓你們吃驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都沒說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是肯定…爸爸會很開心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能見到小朔和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星爸爸的手很大  總是開著不知道是真是假的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時也會跟我和美星一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡美星  總是看著天空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我離開這個小鎮以後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為小鎮還像原來一樣沒有變化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得還會一直保持這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在這個小鎮裡的只有我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的還是會維持原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定大家都會這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小美星說過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年和小朔一起看流星了  好高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…和大家在一起…我想她真的會很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  天已經全黑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星  要來我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來明天也是晴天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  昨天的模擬考試好難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實話說在校外考試還是頭一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是近江同學介紹我去的補習學校的考試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在近江同學旁邊的是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是所謂的應試戰爭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看  好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天部長從近江同學那裡拿來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水星凌日的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我們也要加油了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遲來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我今天要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我…我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔？  江戶川同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法  對大家來說那還只是前一天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:10:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是想要逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是不知道該如何面對她的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美總是在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  我能做的事是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請帶回各自班級討論
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖了這麼晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到以前從來沒有感覺過的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發愣的靈氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修學旅行的手信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是前天給他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過遲了一晚而已…卻感覺已經失去了時機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給男生送書簽當手信…不會有什麼奇怪的意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼了…當我沒說過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣隨著天亮而會變得漸漸難以送出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡讀過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點送給他吧  只不過是手信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有其它意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚學姐  來得剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文部的樣子好像怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文部  早就很怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同學和美星學姐他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然間變得很恩愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔  我是蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.38,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  美星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注視著美星學姐的那厭倦的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前都沒有出現過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  又變得更難送出了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天之內還送不出去的話  就不送了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委員會的工作嗎  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你一下可以嗎  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  會長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是眼鏡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用介意  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到家的話還有後備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉成同學和和泉同學都已經回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  就這樣回去沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  那是校長像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣被明野看到的話會不會想歪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…和美星同一間小學的話應該是經過住宅區的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前住地方也是那邊的住宅區
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小美…美星同一間公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在啊  伊藤商店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡變成了公寓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊樂設備好小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  不由得…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是看不到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到了這個小鎮後  都沒有好好地追尋昔日的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:15:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不早點來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就不待在這個小鎮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡壞掉真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  北海道的手信  兼文化祭的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也有很多不懂的地方  但不介意的話可以找我商量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在的臉  我不想看到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Papo君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  琴塚學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同學？  真巧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們才是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來就我們來送
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以找你商量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔  今天也沒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明上次考試的時候大家都集中起來溫習
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔在生我氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我隱瞞了他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是傳達不了「我很精神  不用擔心」了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  叫別人不要擔心的時候要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少還是有點限制  但好像已經被認可使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好地想  就只有「這次」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:07.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的要這樣做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已經做好調查了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也都問了其他學校的人  確定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是令人費解呢  天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那趕快來準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩…剩下的我自己來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係  我們也想幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真熱心呢  明野會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直到最近才知道  美星的爸爸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼地仰慕他  所以絕不會覺得沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定做了很多無神經的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小美…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說她很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起看流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上幾乎沒有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在電話裡說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了這些之後  我所力所能及的就只有這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情我們都聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大八木同學你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能抑止一定要做些什麼的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幹那種事的話也算上我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜學姐  部長？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家  要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  我該怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔  我說啊  我…很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的事也不是不想告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來雖然很那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是流星雨的團體觀測會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就能夠好好地一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試的忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是雙子座流星雨的極大日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…大家都偷偷地做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞞著我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我就只能想出這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很寂寞  很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是不想遇到壞天氣而讓你失望而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我也知道這樣完全不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  明明是個老女人為什麼要這麼哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看  可以坐在被爐裡吃著蜜柑看星星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  大家都為我舉辦了觀測會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著要一起來看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星  有很多星星在流動著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天美星能和大家一起看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(331,435)}Pollux
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21分30秒  北河三方向2等級
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說起來  還真是超現實啊  這個畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好溫暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  小朔  我經常從小朔的嘴邊聽到爸爸的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到現在爸爸就活在小朔的心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我不是故意隱瞞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  牽起手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您那裡的天空是怎樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好  很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡  大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛的力量  這是愛的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我從剛才就在說  他們兩個沒有在交往的哦
