Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:59.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是實現的 First-step First-sign
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:03.79,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是你喜歡的事吧？
